521	## Constraints
522	
523	- Staged files are NOT part of the inbox/knowledge/archive lifecycle. `consolidate-memory.ts` must NOT process them. Verify that the consolidation tool's directory scanning skips `staged/`.
524	- The sync function follows the same pattern as `syncMemories()` — hash-based, incremental, orphan removal.
525	- Frontmatter parsing uses the simple regex approach (consistent with how other memory files are parsed). Do not add a YAML parser dependency.
